description:
Elizabeth Olsen (Avengers: Infinity War) joins Everything Iconic to talk to Danny about her movie career, Real Housewives, Disney movies, Queer Eye, and so much more. Danny also recaps Drag Race, debates whether or not Tom Cruise is sexy, and expresses his anger over Cameron Diaz retiring. 

Bonus Episodes: www.Patreon.com/EverythingIconic Web: www.EverythingIconic.com Twitter: www.Twitter.com/DannyPellegrino Instagram: www.Instagram.com/DannyPellegrino Facebook: www.Facebook.com/PellegrinoDanny
